{
  "doc_id": "37542",
  "text": "We have implemented a series of programs, lexical resources, and grammars to process interviews and other types of textual data in Spanish. We are using the GATE system [CITATION_1] as an infrastructure or development framework; most developments are new, not included in the GATE system, and they are packaged in a plug-in which can be accessed through the GATE system or used standalone. We have developed various programs to automatically annotate the interviews including segmentation of the transcription, word-based thematic segmentation, tagging, and dictionary-based interpretation and analysis.",
